Params: {2: 'Roland', 3: 'I was going to buy myself some time—w-with a trick or two...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'But this antigen is—a-affecting me—w-way more than I thought it would...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "My power's not recovering—a-and I got teased by that Kamui...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "Couldn't have guessed that after—T-Tenebrion and he... has merged, his strength...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'At the end of the day—I-I got into this mess—b-because I underestimated this "golden antigen."', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "I've got to move the threat levels of her and this Golden Vortex up—a-after I'm back.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "(A large amount of antigen rises from the floor) ...I've been found!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: "Nat's holographic image appears in the air..."}
{2: 'Nat', 3: 'I am honored to find an Ascendant among us!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nat', 3: 'I wonder if you are satisfied with my reception earlier?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nat', 3: 'Oh, I am terribly sorry for this misunderstanding. Here, let me make it up to you...', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Nat', 3: 'I have been fixing up this workshop for a very long time. I would never be lax when it comes to greeting an Ascendant. I hope you find it the most enjoyable! Feel free to let me know any complaints you have!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: "Before Roland can speak, Nat's hologram disappears amidst the golden mist."}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'The power... of the Punishing Virus... is fading...', 4: '1'}
